title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync
description: When exporting a directory (project) and placing the exported JAR in the same directory (project), an out of sync message is displayed when overwriting the exported JAR file for the second time.
OB: When overwriting the exported JAR file for the second time, an out of sync message is displayed.
EB: The software should not display an out of sync message when overwriting the exported JAR file.
SR:
1. Export a directory (project).
2. Place the exported JAR in the same directory (project).
3. Overwrite the exported JAR file for the second time.
